\c 11
\s AmaIsrayeli akhethiweyo nguNkulunkulu ayasindiswa
\p
\v 1 Ngakho ngithi: UNkulunkulu ubalahlile yini abantu bakhe\x + 1 Sam. 12.22. Jer. 31.37.\x*? Phinde\x + Luka 20.16.\x*! Ngoba lami ngingumIsrayeli, owenzalo kaAbrahama\x + Fil. 3.5.\x*\x + 2 Kor. 11.22. Seb. 22.3.\x*, wesizwe sikaBhenjamini\x + Fil. 3.5.\x*.
\v 2 UNkulunkulu kabalahlanga abantu bakhe\x + Hlab. 94.14.\x* abazi ngaphambili\x + 8.29.\x*. Kumbe kalazi yini kuElija ukuthi umbhalo uthini? Ukuthi walabhela njani kuNkulunkulu emelene loIsrayeli\x + Seb. 25.24.\x*, esithi:
\v 3 Nkosi, babulele abaprofethi bakho, badilizile amalathi akho; mina-ke ngisele ngedwa, sebedinga umphefumulo wami\x + 1 Kho. 19.10,14.\x*.
\v 4 Kodwa impendulo kaNkulunkulu yathini kuye? \add Yathi\add*: Ngizitshiyele amadoda azinkulungwane eziyisikhombisa, angaguqanga ngedolo kuBhali\x + 1 Kho. 19.18.\x*.
\v 5 Kunjalo-ke kukhona langalesisikhathi insali ngokukhetha komusa\x + 9.27.\x*.
\v 6 Kodwa uba kungomusa, kakusayi ngemisebenzi; uba kungenjalo umusa kawuseyiwo umusa. Kodwa aluba kusiya ngemisebenzi, kakuseyiwo umusa; uba kungenjalo umsebenzi kawusengumsebenzi\x + 4.4,5. Gal. 5.4. Dute. 9.4,5.\x*.
\v 7 Pho-ke? Lokhu uIsrayeli ayekudinga, lokho kakutholanga, kodwa abakhethiweyo bakuthola, labanye benziwa baba lukhuni\x + 9.31. 10.3.\x*;
\v 8 njengokulotshiweyo \add ukuthi\add*: UNkulunkulu wabanika umoya wobuthongo obukhulu\x + Isa. 29.10.\x*, amehlo ukuze bangaboni, lendlebe ukuze bangezwa, kuze kube lusuku lwalamuhla\x + Isa. 6.9. Mat. 13.14.\x*.
\v 9 LoDavida uthi: Itafula labo libe ngumjibila lesifu\x + Hlab. 69.22,23.\x*, lesikhubekiso, lempindiselo kibo;
\v 10 amehlo abo kafiphazwe ukuze bangaboni, njalo ugobise umhlana wabo njalonjalo\x + 14.13.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Ngakho ngithi: Bakhubeka ukuze bawe yini? Phinde\x + Luka 20.16.\x*! Kodwa ngesiphambeko sabo usindiso \add lufikile\add* kwabezizwe\x + Seb. 28.28.\x*, ukubavusela umona\x + 10.19. 11.14.\x*.
\v 12 Kodwa uba isiphambeko sabo siyinotho yomhlaba, lokwehluleka kwabo kuyinotho yabezizwe, kakhulu kangakanani ukugcwala kwabo?
\s Usindiso lwafika kwabezizwe
\p
\v 13 Ngoba ngikhuluma lani bezizwe, njengalokho mina ngingumphostoli wabezizwe; ngikhulisa inkonzo yami\x + 15.16. Seb. 9.15.\x*;
\v 14 ukuthi mhlawumbe ngibavusele umona \add abe\add*nyama yami\x + 10.19. 11.14.\x*, ngisindise\x + 1 Kor. 9.22.\x* abanye babo\x + 1 Kor. 7.16. 10.33. 1 Tim. 4.16. Jak. 5.20.\x*\x + 1 Kor. 9.22.\x*.
\v 15 Ngoba uba ukulahlwa kwabo kuyikubuyiswa komhlaba, ku\add nga\add*ba yini ukwemukelwa, ngaphandle kokuthi kuyimpilo kwabafileyo\x + 5.11.\x*?
\v 16 Njalo uba izithelo zokuqala zingcwele\x + Levi 23.10.\x*, lenhlama \add injalo\x + Nani 15.19,20.\x*\add*; uba-ke impande ingcwele, lengatsha \add zinjalo\x + Jobe 18.16.\x*\add*.
\v 17 Kodwa uba kwephulwe ezinye ingatsha\x + Jer. 11.16. Joha. 15.2.\x*, lawe ongumhlwathi weganga waxhunyelelwa phakathi kwazo\x + Efe. 2.12.\x*, uhlanganyele lazo impande lamafutha omhlwathi\x + Hlab. 52.8.\x*,
\v 18 ungazincomi phezu kwengatsha; kodwa uba uzincoma phezu \add kwazo\add*, kayisuwe othwele impande, kodwa impande wena.
\v 19 Uzakuthi-ke: Ingatsha zephulwa, ukuze mina ngixhunyelwe.
\v 20 Kulungile; zephulwa ngokungakholwa, wena-ke umi ngokholo\x + 1 Kor. 10.12. 2 Kor. 1.24. Roma 12.3.\x*. Ungazikhukhumezi\x + 1 Kor. 10.12. 2 Kor. 1.24. Roma 12.3.\x*, kodwa yesaba\x + Zaga 28.14. Fil. 2.12. 1 Pet. 1.17. 3.15.\x*;
\v 21 ngoba uba uNkulunkulu engayekelanga ingatsha zemvelo, hlezi lawe kayikukuyekela.
\v 22 Khangela-ke ububele lobukhali bukaNkulunkulu; ubukhali, kulabo abawayo; kodwa kuwe, ububele, uba uhlala ebubeleni\x + Heb. 3.6.\x*; uba kungenjalo uzaqunywa lawe\x + Joha. 15.2.\x*.
\v 23 Lalabo futhi, uba bengahlali ekungakholweni, bazaxhunyelwa, ngoba uNkulunkulu ulamandla okubuya abaxhume.
\v 24 Ngoba uba wena waqunywa emhlwathini weganga ngemvelo, wasuxhunyelelwa ngokuphambene lemvelo emhlwathini ohlanyelweyo, kakhulu kangakanani labo, aba\add zingatsha\add* ngemvelo, bazaxhunyelelwa esihlahleni sakibo somhlwathi\x + 2 Kor. 3.16.\x*?
\s UNkulunkulu ulesihawu kubantu bonke
\p
\v 25 Ngoba ngithanda ukuthi lingabi ngabangaziyo, bazalwane, ngalimfihlo\x + 1 Kor. 10. 1.\x*, hlezi lizitshaye abahlakaniphileyo\x + 12.16.\x*, ukuthi ubulukhuni\x + 2 Kor. 3.14.\x* sebehlele uIsrayeli nganxanye\x + 15.15.\x*, kuze kungene ukugcwala kwabezizwe\x + Luka 21.24. Isam. 7.9.\x*;
\v 26 ngokunjalo-ke uIsrayeli wonke uzasindiswa\x + 2 Kor. 3.16.\x*; njengokulotshiweyo \add ukuthi\add*: Kuzavela\x + Isa. 59.20,21.\x* eSiyoni uMkhululi\x + Hlab. 14.7. 53.6.\x*, asuse ukungabi loNkulunkulu kuJakobe\x + Seb. 3.26.\x*;
\v 27 njalo yilesi isivumelwano sami kibo, lapho ngizasusa izono zabo\x + Isa. 27.9.\x*.
\v 28 Ngokwevangeli bayizitha ngenxa yenu; kodwa ngokukhetha bangabathandiweyo ngenxa yabobaba\x + Dute. 7.8. 9.5. 10.15. Roma 9.5.\x*;
\v 29 ngoba izipho zomusa lokubiza kukaNkulunkulu\x + 3.3.\x* kakulakuphenduka\x + 2 Kor. 7.10. Nani 23.19.\x*.
\v 30 Ngoba njengalokhu lani kade lingamlaleli uNkulunkulu\x + Efe. 2.2.\x*, kodwa khathesi selihawukelwe ngenxa yokungalaleli kwabo;
\v 31 ngokunjalo lalabo khathesi kabalalelanga, ukuze ngesihawu senu bahawukelwe labo\x + 11.25.\x*;
\v 32 ngoba uNkulunkulu ubavalele bonke ekungalalelini, ukuze abe lesihawu kibo bonke\x + Gal. 3.22. Roma 3.9.\x*.
\v 33 Yeka ukujula kwenotho\x + Hlab. 92.5. Tshu. 7.24.\x*, kokubili eyenhlakanipho\x + Hlab. 92.5. Tshu. 7.24.\x* leyolwazi lukaNkulunkulu\x + Hlab. 139.6.\x*! Kakuphenyeki kangakanani ukwahlulela kwakhe\x + Jobe 5.9. 11.7. 28.14. Hlab. 36.6. 2.\x*, lendlela zakhe\x + Dute. 29.29. Zaga 25.2.\x* kazilandeleki\x + Efe. 3.8.\x*!
\v 34 Ngoba ngubani owazi ingqondo yeNkosi? Kumbe ngubani owaba ngumeluleki wayo\x + Isa. 40.13. Jobe 15.8. 21.22. 36.22. 40.2. Jer. 23.18. 1 Kor. 2.16.\x*?
\v 35 Kumbe ngubani owamnika kuqala, njalo kubuyiselwe kuye\x + Jobe 41.11. Jobe 35.7. Hlab. 16.2.\x*?
\v 36 Ngoba konke kuvela kuye\x + 1 Kor. 8.6. 11.12.\x*, \add ku\add*ngaye\x + 1 Kor. 8.6. Kol. 1.16. Zaga 16.4.\x*, \add ku\add*ya kuye\x + 1 Kor. 8.6. Kol. 1.16. Zaga 16.4.\x*; \add kabube\add* kuye ubukhosi kuze kube nininini. Ameni\x + Gal. 1.5. 1 Tim. 1.17. 2 Tim. 4.18. Heb. 13.21. 1 Pet. 4.11. 5.11. 2 Pet. 3.18. Juda 25. Isam. 1.6.\x*.
